_sText:
This is a simple selfservice gas station.
might have some flaws or things missing.
i didnt want to work on it anymore.

since this is an unmanned self service station, there had to an atm like machine for payment.
i didnt find one in the models readily available with hl2/css so i used an optical scanner instead.
i was too lazy to model one, sorry.

this prefab as is, is nothing more than decoration imho.
you may do with this as you see fit.
if you decide to use this please send me an email / pm i would like to see it :)
